  "comment": "The EclProfile FWHPVW elevates the benchmark in LED ellipsoidals by delivering 450 Watts of fixture power, effectively doubling its lumen output to an impressive 15,500 lumens. Retaining the renowned VaribleWhite LED engine of the FW series, it offers superior color rendering for unparalleled light quality. Specifically designed for longer throw distances and higher hanging positions, the FWHP is the ideal replacement for traditional HPL 750W and 2kW tungsten fixtures, excelling in large venues such as theaters, studios, and auditoriums.",
